title: Bunkercast VI: Rams Release Todd Gurley
itunes:title: Bunkercast VI: Rams Release Todd Gurley
description:
A webcast filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler recap the latest with this free agency frenzy. They breakdown the Rams and Todd Gurley parting ways and the Eagles offseason moves.
